Manchester United's new signing Radamel Falcao has revealed that he will be fulfilling a dream by playing in the Premier League this season.

The Colombian striker sealed a shock £6million season-long move to United on Monday and will wear the No 9 shirt for Louis van Gaal's side.

Speaking to MUTV, Falcao said: 'I am very happy to be part of this big club. I’ve waited for this moment during a lot of the year. Now I am a player of Manchester United.

